{
  "stem": "17625.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, I walked from one man to the other and explained to him that I had my sister in Libiaz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I have a sister living in Libiaz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not-- he didn't-- I got a winter hat and I got a-- a three-quarter coat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so if he would pull off the hat, he would see I'm shaven, but he didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one to the other until we came to the end of the-- of the road, where the Howitzer was there, and it was hidden with-- under the trees.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he gave us permission to go to the sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So outside were a sled-- was a sled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were there were [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Silesia, it was-- the-- the Germans there were [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were-- they were living on the border between Germany and Poland, was-- they called us [NON-ENGLISH] because Silesia was-- was-- was half Poland and-- [INAUDIBLE] was half Poland, half German.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he explained it to me, you are lucky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You are lucky, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You are lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You went to [? no man's ?] [? land here. ?] OK.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we came to Libiaz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I-- I was glad that didn't ask me where-- where I want to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I went down, I came into this-- to this guy, a customer, [INAUDIBLE], a nice guy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I came in into him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This-and-this.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When he saw me, he started trembling, I didn't mean to hurt you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But this is [INAUDIBLE] life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I-- I-- I risk all my family here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Here is a soup.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Here is bread, but go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were walking-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] all the time till we came to Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
